<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= statusCode %> - Error</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 72px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .error-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .error-description {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #495057;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .back-link {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-code"><%= statusCode %></div>
        <div class="error-message"><%= message %></div>
        <div class="error-description">
            <p>We're sorry, but the page you are looking for might have been moved or deleted.</p>
            <p>Try going back to the <a href="/" class="back-link">homepage</a> or check your URL.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
